Cewl - create custom password lists from the target website

Syntax:
  cewl -d <depth to spider> -m <minimum word length> -w <output wordlist> <url of website>

Commands:
  cewl -w wordlist.txt -d 5 -m 5 <URL>

Options:
  -w    Write the contents to a file.
  -m 5  Gathers strings (words) that are 5 characters or more
  -d 5  Depth level of web crawling/spidering (default 2)
  --lowercase   words in lowercase
  -e    Extract emails from websites. It's helpful to get this information when phishing, password spraying, or brute-forcing passwords later.